	Title: Playtest 20200329
	Author: Lukas Franke
	Content: Playtest 20200329 is out for testing. Changes include:\n\n  • Restored right-click scrolling support\n  • Fixed aircraft not taking off when no rallypoint is set\n  • Pathfinding improvements\n  • Reworked airstrip exits to prevent traffic jams\n  • Fixed spicebloom behaviour in Dune 2000\n  • Additional campaign missions\n  • Community balance changes for Red Alert\n\nVisit www.openra.net for more information and to download the new playtest. We hope you enjoy it!
